Class Summary
ExtractDataHolder Holds reference to a particular data element from the data store.

StudentDetailsExtractor Handles the extraction of the students details from the underlying persistence mechanism in Openmark so that their details can be reused within another environment (at this time for testing if they have problems) Equally can be reused for other purposes in the future.
